title: Learn Data Skills
text:
Preface
Welcome to Learn Data Skills!

title: 1  Introduction
text: This book is going to be a personal, and hopefully, community project to develop a compltely free and open source set of materials for learning data relevant skills and techniques that are practical and modern for real world problem solving.

title: 2  Summary
text: This book will be built using completely free and open source materials powered by community knowledge and experience with data.

title: 3  Books
text:
